          partner_faq = [
            ["Is the AI replacing our admissions coordinator?",
             "No. HosAlivio is the front-door triage layer; it acknowledges every family message in seconds, classifies urgency, and pages the right human. Your coordinator stops drowning in 2 a.m. pages and gets to focus on the cases that actually need a human."],
            ["How does HosAlivio handle PHI / HIPAA?",
             "Patient data is encrypted at rest with Active Record Encryption (chart fields, notes, addresses), audit-logged via PaperTrail on every write, and scoped per-agency via ActsAsTenant. We sign a BAA before any agency goes live."],
            ["Does it integrate with our EMR?",
             "Yes. Homecare Homebase, Netsmart, MatrixCare, and WellSky are first-class. You can also run HosAlivio standalone if you'd rather not bridge a System of Record."],
            ["What about the Notice of Election deadline?",
             "The 5-day NOE clock starts the moment the MD certifies. HosAlivio's insurance agent watches it, flags overdue at 4 days, and auto-files when authorized. No more late submissions costing you the benefit period."],
